 Weapons storage management; 
 Ammunition and explosives storage management; 
 Accounting for weapons and ammunition; 
 Transportation of weapons; 
 Transportation of ammunition; 
 Storage checks; 
 Reporting and investigating loss or theft; 
 Destruction of weapons (or other appropriate methods of disposal and potential marking); 
 Destruction of ammunition (or other appropriate methods of disposal). 
 Managing spontaneous disarmament, including in advance of a formal DDR process.

